
                   Mme. Brown is a very sweet lady. She may come off as hard to others but if you pay attention and are active in class it is better. The tests are pretty hard but the homework is very easy.
                
                   Dr. Ragucci is a great woman who loves teaching. She is always willing to help and cares about her students! With that said you have to do the homework and show up to class. You're learning a language, requires practice and some outside devotion. Overall though its not bad! The homework is easy and if you need extra time on it she usually gives it!
                
