                   Dr. Ragucci is an awesome professor. Very friendly and clearly enjoys teaching. You cannot do well on the exams unless you study thoroughly but that's the case with any language. Overall, she's a clear lecturer and very patient which comes in handy when you try to express yourself in French. She's everyone's favorite french prof for good reason.
                
                   Dr. Ragucci was an awesome professor. She explained everything in english before moving on to strictly speaking in french. On written compositions she gave you a chance to correct the original before turning in the final draft. She was also very helpful when trying to speak in french during the lecture. She made lectures pretty interesting as well.
                
                   She's great for teaching English to French but if you speak Spanish and learn rough Spanish connections then I wouldn't take her. She is French so she knows the language. The online he isn't too bad but if you don't do it it piles up.
                
